<br>
I am Dukvodju Runecake. The First Tank Wizard of Ak'anon. President of the Tank Wizards Union. Champion of the King of Ak'anon and Co-Leader of the Gnomish Alliance of Gnomes.<br>
<br>
I will share with you only this wisdom: Practice when young at least 2 weapon skills. Build your skills to their maximum. Always carry a melee weapon (doesn't necessarily have to be wielded). There may come a time that it will save your life. The simple truth is: without mana, we are NOTHING !!! That is why you must have knowledge of the weapon crafts!<br>
<br>
For all those that say don't worry about melee once you are of veteran status ... Humbug !!! Shame on you for steering the young ones down the dark path. There has not been a day where I have not used a weapon in melee combat.<br>
<br>
There have been many a dire situation where I have charged into battle to face the onslaught of our enemy so that I might save the life of a friend. Granted the occassional effort is futile but my record holds and so does my reputation. I will always be there to save a life. Just because I'm out of mana doesn't mean I can't make a difference. <br>
